                    </div>
                    <span>Masterfully written, this book immediately touches one's heart. Rain, the central character, takes us through her long journey to her new adopted family, crossing continents and cultural boundaries, and teaches us, in a way that only a child can, the power and poignancy of a family's love.<P>Through this book, we are reminded that a family's love really is forever.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Brought a tear to my eye...great for all ages!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
